name: Art Lite (Tracey)
description:
Lo-tech Lava Lamp.

Switched on and off by finger pressure applied at the top.  LED light runs on batteries (3 x AAA) - first set provided.

Lid at bottom allows easy access for replacing batteries.

All parts plastic, apart from light.

Height 16 cm.  Largest diameter 10.8 cm.

Weight 114 g.
